6. Governance and Review
The Security Lead updates the Risk Treatment Plan regularly (e.g., quarterly), in sync with the Risk Register.

Progress is reviewed in security/risk review meetings with leadership.

When actions are completed, the corresponding Status and Residual Risk Rating are updated.

Any accepted risks are explicitly documented and revisited at least annually.

